A simple generator for generating karma (http://wiki.sugarlabs.org/go/Karma)
lessons.

The main script is generate-karma-lesson.py. To get some help about the
different options:
./generate-karma-lesson.py --help

The templates directory contains the templates that are used by the
individual lessons in the lessons directory.

An example of generating a lesson:
./generate-karma-lesson.py lessons/what-is-this-word/description.py

Point your browser at deploy/Activities/6_English_whatsThisWord_1_K/index.html
to run the lesson.

To generate all lessons:
./generate-karma-lesson.py -a
